div.h2: Algorithm: From Token IDs to Attention Mask

div.p: 0 = PAD token ID Non-zero = real tokens
Why? Attention scores are [batch, seq, seq]. Need [batch, 1, seq] to broadcast across query dimension.
Key insight: Padding positions get zero attention weight. Rows still sum to 1.0 (valid probability distribution).
